* * *Dear Prudence,My long-term boyfriend works as a professional film crew member with long hours and an unpredictable schedule.
You say that it’s not uncommon for “crew people” to hook up on shoots, but your boyfriend isn’t “crew people.” He’s your boyfriend.
* * *Dear Prudence,My boyfriend is amazing, but his parents have a loose concept of hygiene.
I don’t think “Honey, I’ve lied to you for years” would go over too well.
I don’t think you’re doing anything wrong.